<solution>
<p><ul><li>7.5002074282735</li></ul></p><p><m>\displaystyle{P}{\left({t}\right)}={1600}{e}^{{{0.2}{t}}}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle{7171}={1600}{e}^{{{0.2}{t}}}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle\frac{{7171}}{{1600}}={e}^{{{0.2}{t}}}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle{\ln{{\left(\frac{{7171}}{{1600}}\right)}}}={0.2}{t}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle\frac{{\ln{{\left(\frac{{7171}}{{1600}}\right)}}}}{{0.2}}={t}</m></p>
<p>
<m>\displaystyle{t}={7.5002074282735}</m></p>
</solution>
